---
title: Chicken Pot Pie Pasta with Mushrooms and Peas
description: We've reimagined a comforting pot pie in easy pasta form! This lightened version retains all the same great flavours, plus it's served with fusilli that's great for catching all the delectable sauce!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pates-style-pate-au-poulet-2e4ec328.jpg
